</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="73" type="food_feeding">
<paragraph blockId="7.[163,1371,873,1693]" pageId="7" pageNumber="73">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[164,426,1152,1181]" pageId="7" pageNumber="73">Food and Feeding.</emphasis>
There is no specific information available for this species, but it is presumably largely folivorous.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
